column5: Didn't go to school today cause I was sick so I fooled aorund and decided to make a slideshow. Their are lots of old photos and some photos that should be in the summer section are in spring. I didn't get to pick my own music ethier so here's it is...

Nice slide show.  If you want it to play directly in the forum topic just switch the "Post Options" at the bottom to "HTML On - Auto Linebreak Mode" and then paste in the HTML tag in the list of photo bucket options and you'll get something like this:  <embed width="448" height="361" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" wmode="transparent" src="http://i63.photobucket.com/remix/player.swf?videoURL=http%3A%2F%2Fvid63.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fh136%2Fmikepike_2006%2F30b67f24.pbr&hostname=stream63.photobucket.com"></embed>
